nodes.text: Tryki was a former female Zabrak pirate who was arrested for attempting to board a First Order cruiser near Rakata Prime. Her starship was destroyed, but she escaped and eventually joined the Zendiat Collective, a criminal group led by Zool Zendiat. At some point, the group attacked Niima Outpost on Jakku and took the junk boss Unkar Plutt as hostage for questioning about the head of a J9 droid.
